{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance-- before-- ah, how they-- they had in dollars, mostly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In dollars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sewn in.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On their body or-- or-- you know, rings, or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you that my mother had an American bank.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother didn't believe in-- in presents like like, you know, rings, or jewelry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was from a poor, quite-- I wouldn't say poor, but poorer background.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she believed in money, or in-- sort of-- she got some money, she bought a block of [? lead. ?] Did you-- did you hear about another woman who would get money for her birthday, and buy-- or anniversary-- and buy a block of-- give a deposit for a block of [? lead? ?]",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or, she also believed in American bank, which was one in-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she used to collect money and put it, because she-- she was, herself, she was-- I wouldn't say mean, she wasn't mean.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was brought up in that way that she looked after the money, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She wasn't just going and getting rid of the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In an American bank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when the Germans-- until she understood that she has to take it out, she didn't have time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans put their hand on it and paid her in a few pennies, and make her to sign that she got the money back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you asked me about the money, so I just recalled, it's-- I'm talking about a later time, but you reminded me of that incident.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what was your question?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, we didn't have so much money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But grandfather had, because grandfather collected everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
